<v-container fluid grid-list-xl>
  <v-layout align-center wrap>
    <v-flex xs12 sm12 md3 d-flex v-if="com_nota== true">
      <v-select
        color="teal darken-3"
        :items="empresas"
        label="Empresa*"
        outline
        append-icon="fas fa-building"
        v-model="empresa"
        :rules="[() => !!empresa || 'Este campo precisa ser selecionado!']"
      ></v-select>
      <cad-empresa v-on:empresas="AtualizarEmpresas()"></cad-empresa>
    </v-flex>
    <v-flex xs12 sm12 md3 d-flex v-if="com_nota == true">
      <v-dialog
        ref="dialog_compra"
        v-model="modal_compra"
        :return-value.sync="data_compra"
        persistent
        lazy
        full-width
        width="290px"
      >
        <v-text-field
          slot="activator"
          v-model="computedDateFormatted"
          label="Data da compra *"
          append-icon="event"
          readonly
          color="teal darken-3"
          hint
          persistent-hint
          outline
        ></v-text-field>
        <v-date-picker v-model="data_compra" scrollable locale="pt-BR">
          <v-spacer></v-spacer>
          <v-btn flat color="primary" @click="modal_compra = false">Cancelar</v-btn>
          <v-btn flat color="primary" @click="$refs.dialog_compra.save(data_compra)">OK</v-btn>
        </v-date-picker>
      </v-dialog>
    </v-flex>
    <v-flex xs12 sm12 md6 offset-md3 d-flex v-if="com_nota == false">
      <v-dialog
        ref="dialog_compra"
        v-model="modal_compra"
        :return-value.sync="data_compra"
        persistent
        lazy
        full-width
        width="290px"
      >
        <v-text-field
          slot="activator"
          v-model="computedDateFormatted"
          label="Data da compra *"
          append-icon="event"
          readonly
          color="teal darken-3"
          hint
          persistent-hint
          outline
        ></v-text-field>
        <v-date-picker v-model="data_compra" scrollable locale="pt-BR">
          <v-spacer></v-spacer>
          <v-btn flat color="primary" @click="modal_compra = false">Cancelar</v-btn>
          <v-btn flat color="primary" @click="$refs.dialog_compra.save(data_compra)">OK</v-btn>
        </v-date-picker>
      </v-dialog>
    </v-flex>
    <v-flex xs12 sm12 md3 d-flex v-if="com_nota == true">
      <v-text-field
        v-money="money"
        v-model.lazy="preco_instrumento"
        outline
        color="teal darken-3"
        append-icon="fas fa-hand-holding-usd"
        label="Valor do instrumento*"
      ></v-text-field>
    </v-flex>
    <v-flex xs12 sm12 md3 d-flex v-if="com_nota == true">
      <v-text-field
        append-icon="fas fa-signature"
        v-model="nota_fiscal"
        outline
        color="teal darken-3"
        :hint="hint_nota"
        label="Nota Fiscal*"
      ></v-text-field>
    </v-flex>
  </v-layout>
  <v-layout align-center wrap>
    <v-flex xs12 sm6 md3 offset-md3 d-flex>
      <v-checkbox label="Sem data de compra." @change="SemDataCompra()"></v-checkbox>
    </v-flex>
    <v-flex xs12 sm6 md3 offset-md3 d-flex>
      <v-checkbox label="Sem nota fiscal." @change="SemNotaCompra()"></v-checkbox>
    </v-flex>
  </v-layout>

  <v-flex sm5 md5 lg5 offset-sm4>
    <cad-notap
      v-on:cadastrarCompra="CadastrarCompra"
      v-bind:numero_tombamento="numero_do_instrumento"
      v-show="com_nota"
    ></cad-notap>
  </v-flex>
  <v-flex sm5 md5 lg5 offset-sm4 v-if="com_nota == false">
    <v-flex sm12 md12 xs12 lg12 align-center>
      <v-btn round outline color="teal darken-2" dark v-on:click="CadastrarCompra">
        SALVAR INSTRUMENTO
        <v-icon right dark>fas fa-save</v-icon>
      </v-btn>
    </v-flex>
  </v-flex>
</v-container>
